## Important Rules
- NEVER use `git status -uall` (can OOM on large repos)
- Pi user is `pi`, NOT `james`
- EVO user is `james`, NOT `pi`
- Pi project path is `~/clawdbot/` (NOT `~/clawdbot-claude-code/`)
- SCP overwrites, doesn't merge — send individual files, not directories
- After deploying Node.js files, ALWAYS restart: `sudo systemctl restart clawdbot`
- Dashboard is a Rust/egui native app, NOT HTML/Chromium
- Direct ethernet between Pi and EVO: Pi=10.0.0.1, EVO=10.0.0.2 (0.4ms latency)
- Bot code uses `src/evo-llm.js` for EVO communication (OpenAI-compatible API)
- After changing **both** `memory-service/main.py` and `command_router.py`, redeploy both files and restart `clawdbot-memory` on EVO
